SELECT [e].[EndTime], [e].[LessonId], [t0].[Id] AS [LessonPracticeId], [e].[Name]
FROM [Contests] AS [e]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [e0].*
    FROM [Lessons] AS [e0]
    WHERE [e0].[IsDeleted] = 0
) AS [t] ON [e].[LessonId] = [t].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [e1].*
    FROM [Practices] AS [e1]
    WHERE [e1].[IsDeleted] = 0
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[LessonId]
WHERE (([e].[IsDeleted] = 0) AND ([e].[IsDeleted] = 0)) AND ([e].[EndTime] < GETDATE())

FROM [Submissions] AS [e]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [e0].[Id], [e0].[AllowedMemoryInMegaBytes], [e0].[AllowedMinCodeDifferenceInPercentage], [e0].[AllowedTimeInMilliseconds], [e0].[AutomatedTestingProject], [e0].[CreatedOn], [e0].[DeletedOn], [e0].[IsDeleted], [e0].[IsExtraTask], [e0].[LessonId], [e0].[MaxPoints], [e0].[ModifiedOn], [e0].[Name], [e0].[OrderBy], [e0].[SubmissionType], [e0].[TestingStrategy], [e0].[TimeIntervalBetweenSubmissionInSeconds]
    FROM [Problems] AS [e0]
    WHERE [e0].[IsDeleted] = 0
) AS [t] ON [e].[ProblemId] = [t].[Id]
WHERE ((([e].[IsDeleted] = 0) AND ([e].[IsDeleted] = 0)) AND (([e].[ProblemId] = @__problemId_0) AND ([e].[UserId] = @__userId_1))) AND (((
    SELECT COUNT(*)
    FROM [ExecutedTests] AS [e1]
    WHERE [e].[Id] = [e1].[SubmissionId]
) > 0) OR [e].[CompilationErrors] IS NOT NULL)

SELECT [x.ExecutedTests].[Id], [x.ExecutedTests].[CreatedOn], [x.ExecutedTests].[Error], [x.ExecutedTests].[ExecutionResultType], [x.ExecutedTests].[IsCorrect], [x.ExecutedTests].[MemoryUsed], [x.ExecutedTests].[ModifiedOn], [x.ExecutedTests].[Output], [x.ExecutedTests].[SubmissionId], [x.ExecutedTests].[TestId], [x.ExecutedTests].[TimeUsed]
FROM [ExecutedTests] AS [x.ExecutedTests]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT DISTINCT [t1].*
    FROM (
        SELECT [e2].[Id], [e2].[SubmisionDate]
        FROM [Submissions] AS [e2]
        INNER JOIN (
            SELECT [e3].*
            FROM [Problems] AS [e3]
            WHERE [e3].[IsDeleted] = 0
        ) AS [t0] ON [e2].[ProblemId] = [t0].[Id]
        WHERE ((([e2].[IsDeleted] = 0) AND ([e2].[IsDeleted] = 0)) AND (([e2].[ProblemId] = @__problemId_0) AND ([e2].[UserId] = @__userId_1))) AND (((
            SELECT COUNT(*)
            FROM [ExecutedTests] AS [e4]
            WHERE [e2].[Id] = [e4].[SubmissionId]
        ) > 0) OR [e2].[CompilationErrors] IS NOT NULL)
        ORDER BY [e2].[SubmisionDate] DESC, [e2].[Id]
        OFFSET @__p_2 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_3 ROWS ONLY
    ) AS [t1]

2022-01-05 09:49:20.667 +02:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (0ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [e].[EndTime], [e].[LessonId], [t0].[Id] AS [LessonPracticeId], [e].[Name]
FROM [Contests] AS [e]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [e0].*
    FROM [Lessons] AS [e0]
    WHERE [e0].[IsDeleted] = 0
) AS [t] ON [e].[LessonId] = [t].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [e1].*
    FROM [Practices] AS [e1]
    WHERE [e1].[IsDeleted] = 0

        FROM [Submissions] AS [e3]
        INNER JOIN (
            SELECT [e4].*
            FROM [Problems] AS [e4]
            WHERE [e4].[IsDeleted] = 0
        ) AS [t1] ON [e3].[ProblemId] = [t1].[Id]
        WHERE (([e3].[IsDeleted] = 0) AND (([e3].[UserId] = @__userId_0) AND ([t1].[IsExtraTask] = 0))) AND ([t].[Id] = [e3].[ContestId])
        GROUP BY [e3].[ProblemId]
    ) AS [t2]
) AS [ActualPoints], (
    SELECT SUM([e5].[MaxPoints])
    FROM [Problems] AS [e5]
    WHERE (([e5].[IsDeleted] = 0) AND ([e5].[IsExtraTask] = 0)) AND ([t0].[Id] = [e5].[LessonId])
) AS [MaxPoints], [t].[Name] AS [ContestName], [t].[LessonId], [x.UserContests].[ContestId]
FROM [AspNetUsers] AS [e]
INNER JOIN [UserContests] AS [x.UserContests] ON [e].[Id] = [x.UserContests].[UserId]

    FROM [Contests] AS [e0]
    WHERE [e0].[IsDeleted] = 0
) AS [t] ON [x.UserContests].[ContestId] = [t].[Id]

        SELECT MAX([e3].[ActualPoints]) AS [c]

            FROM [Problems] AS [e4]
            WHERE [e4].[IsDeleted] = 0
        ) AS [t1] ON [e3].[ProblemId] = [t1].[Id]
        WHERE (([e3].[IsDeleted] = 0) AND (([e3].[UserId] = @__userId_0) AND ([t1].[IsExtraTask] = 0))) AND ([t].[Id] = [e3].[PracticeId])
        GROUP BY [e3].[ProblemId]
    ) AS [t2]
) AS [ActualPoints], (
    SELECT SUM([e5].[MaxPoints])
    FROM [Problems] AS [e5]
    WHERE (([e5].[IsDeleted] = 0) AND ([e5].[IsExtraTask] = 0)) AND ([t0].[Id] = [e5].[LessonId])
) AS [MaxPoints], [t0].[Name] AS [LessonName], [x.UserPractices].[PracticeId], [t].[LessonId]

    WHERE [e0].[IsDeleted] = 0

SELECT [e].[EndTime], [e].[LessonId], [t0].[Id] AS [LessonPracticeId], [e].[Name]
FROM [Contests] AS [e]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [e0].*
    FROM [Lessons] AS [e0]
    WHERE [e0].[IsDeleted] = 0
) AS [t] ON [e].[LessonId] = [t].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [e1].*
    FROM [Practices] AS [e1]
    WHERE [e1].[IsDeleted] = 0
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[LessonId]
WHERE (([e].[IsDeleted] = 0) AND ([e].[IsDeleted] = 0)) AND ([e].[EndTime] < GETDATE())

) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[LessonId]

    FROM [Lessons] AS [e0]
    WHERE [e0].[IsDeleted] = 0

FROM [Contests] AS [e]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [e0].*
    FROM [Lessons] AS [e0]
    WHERE [e0].[IsDeleted] = 0
) AS [t] ON [e].[LessonId] = [t].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [e1].*
    FROM [Practices] AS [e1]
    WHERE [e1].[IsDeleted] = 0
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[LessonId]

    FROM [Lessons] AS [e0]
    WHERE [e0].[IsDeleted] = 0

2022-01-05 11:27:01.892 +02:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (2ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [e].[EndTime], [e].[LessonId], [t0].[Id] AS [LessonPracticeId], [e].[Name]
FROM [Contests] AS [e]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [e0].*
    FROM [Lessons] AS [e0]
    WHERE [e0].[IsDeleted] = 0
) AS [t] ON [e].[LessonId] = [t].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [e1].*
    FROM [Practices] AS [e1]
    WHERE [e1].[IsDeleted] = 0
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[LessonId]
WHERE (([e].[IsDeleted] = 0) AND ([e].[IsDeleted] = 0)) AND ([e].[EndTime] < GETDATE())

FROM [Contests] AS [e]

2022-01-05 11:31:32.400 +02:00 [WRN] The LINQ expression 'where ((DateTime.Now - [e].EndTime).Days <= __passedDays_0)' could not be translated and will be evaluated locally.
2022-01-05 11:31:32.412 +02:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (0ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [e].[EndTime], [e].[LessonId], [t0].[Id] AS [LessonPracticeId], [e].[Name]
FROM [Contests] AS [e]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [e0].*
    FROM [Lessons] AS [e0]
    WHERE [e0].[IsDeleted] = 0
) AS [t] ON [e].[LessonId] = [t].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [e1].*
    FROM [Practices] AS [e1]
    WHERE [e1].[IsDeleted] = 0

FROM [Contests] AS [e]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [e0].*
    FROM [Lessons] AS [e0]
    WHERE [e0].[IsDeleted] = 0
) AS [t] ON [e].[LessonId] = [t].[Id]

    SELECT [e1].*
    FROM [Practices] AS [e1]
    WHERE [e1].[IsDeleted] = 0

SELECT [e].[EndTime], [e].[LessonId], [t0].[Id] AS [LessonPracticeId], [e].[Name]
FROM [Contests] AS [e]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [e0].*
    FROM [Lessons] AS [e0]
    WHERE [e0].[IsDeleted] = 0
) AS [t] ON [e].[LessonId] = [t].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [e1].*
    FROM [Practices] AS [e1]
    WHERE [e1].[IsDeleted] = 0
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[LessonId]
WHERE (([e].[IsDeleted] = 0) AND ([e].[IsDeleted] = 0)) AND ([e].[EndTime] < GETDATE())

FROM [Contests] AS [e]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [e0].*
    FROM [Lessons] AS [e0]
    WHERE [e0].[IsDeleted] = 0
) AS [t] ON [e].[LessonId] = [t].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [e1].*
    FROM [Practices] AS [e1]
    WHERE [e1].[IsDeleted] = 0
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[LessonId]

SELECT [e].[EndTime], [e].[LessonId], [t0].[Id] AS [LessonPracticeId], [e].[Name]
FROM [Contests] AS [e]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [e0].*
    FROM [Lessons] AS [e0]
    WHERE [e0].[IsDeleted] = 0
) AS [t] ON [e].[LessonId] = [t].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [e1].*
    FROM [Practices] AS [e1]
    WHERE [e1].[IsDeleted] = 0
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[LessonId]
WHERE (([e].[IsDeleted] = 0) AND ([e].[IsDeleted] = 0)) AND ([e].[EndTime] < GETDATE())

    FROM [Lessons] AS [e0]

2022-01-05 12:28:12.607 +02:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (0ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [e].[EndTime], [e].[LessonId], [t0].[Id] AS [LessonPracticeId], [e].[Name]
FROM [Contests] AS [e]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [e0].*
    FROM [Lessons] AS [e0]
    WHERE [e0].[IsDeleted] = 0
) AS [t] ON [e].[LessonId] = [t].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [e1].*
    FROM [Practices] AS [e1]
    WHERE [e1].[IsDeleted] = 0
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[LessonId]
WHERE (([e].[IsDeleted] = 0) AND ([e].[IsDeleted] = 0)) AND ([e].[EndTime] < GETDATE())

SELECT [e].[EndTime], [e].[LessonId], [t0].[Id] AS [LessonPracticeId], [e].[Name]
FROM [Contests] AS [e]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [e0].*
    FROM [Lessons] AS [e0]
    WHERE [e0].[IsDeleted] = 0
) AS [t] ON [e].[LessonId] = [t].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [e1].*
    FROM [Practices] AS [e1]
    WHERE [e1].[IsDeleted] = 0
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[LessonId]
WHERE (([e].[IsDeleted] = 0) AND ([e].[IsDeleted] = 0)) AND ([e].[EndTime] < GETDATE())

SELECT [e].[EndTime], [e].[LessonId], [t0].[Id] AS [LessonPracticeId], [e].[Name]
FROM [Contests] AS [e]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [e0].*
    FROM [Lessons] AS [e0]
    WHERE [e0].[IsDeleted] = 0
) AS [t] ON [e].[LessonId] = [t].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [e1].*
    FROM [Practices] AS [e1]
    WHERE [e1].[IsDeleted] = 0
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[LessonId]
WHERE (([e].[IsDeleted] = 0) AND ([e].[IsDeleted] = 0)) AND ([e].[EndTime] < GETDATE())

2022-01-05 13:06:27.599 +02:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (5ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [e].[EndTime], [e].[LessonId], [t0].[Id] AS [LessonPracticeId], [e].[Name]
FROM [Contests] AS [e]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [e0].*
    FROM [Lessons] AS [e0]
    WHERE [e0].[IsDeleted] = 0
) AS [t] ON [e].[LessonId] = [t].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [e1].*

        FROM [UserPractices] AS [x]
        WHERE ([x].[UserId] = @__userId_0) AND ([x].[PracticeId] = @__practiceId_1))
    THEN CAST(1 AS BIT) ELSE CAST(0 AS BIT)
END

SELECT [e].[EndTime], [e].[LessonId], [t0].[Id] AS [LessonPracticeId], [e].[Name]
FROM [Contests] AS [e]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [e0].*
    FROM [Lessons] AS [e0]
    WHERE [e0].[IsDeleted] = 0
) AS [t] ON [e].[LessonId] = [t].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [e1].*
    FROM [Practices] AS [e1]
    WHERE [e1].[IsDeleted] = 0
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[LessonId]

    FROM [Lessons] AS [e0]

FROM [ExecutedTests] AS [x.ExecutedTests]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT DISTINCT [t1].*
    FROM (
        SELECT [e2].[Id], [e2].[SubmisionDate]
        FROM [Submissions] AS [e2]
        INNER JOIN (
            SELECT [e3].*
            FROM [Problems] AS [e3]
            WHERE [e3].[IsDeleted] = 0
        ) AS [t0] ON [e2].[ProblemId] = [t0].[Id]
        WHERE ((([e2].[IsDeleted] = 0) AND ([e2].[IsDeleted] = 0)) AND (([e2].[ProblemId] = @__problemId_0) AND ([e2].[UserId] = @__userId_1))) AND (((
            SELECT COUNT(*)
            FROM [ExecutedTests] AS [e4]
            WHERE [e2].[Id] = [e4].[SubmissionId]

        ORDER BY [e2].[SubmisionDate] DESC, [e2].[Id]
        OFFSET @__p_2 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_3 ROWS ONLY
    ) AS [t1]
) AS [t2] ON [x.ExecutedTests].[SubmissionId] = [t2].[Id]
ORDER BY [t2].[SubmisionDate] DESC, [t2].[Id]

    SELECT [e0].[Id], [e0].[AllowedMemoryInMegaBytes], [e0].[AllowedMinCodeDifferenceInPercentage], [e0].[AllowedTimeInMilliseconds], [e0].[AutomatedTestingProject], [e0].[CreatedOn], [e0].[DeletedOn], [e0].[IsDeleted], [e0].[IsExtraTask], [e0].[LessonId], [e0].[MaxPoints], [e0].[ModifiedOn], [e0].[Name], [e0].[OrderBy], [e0].[SubmissionType], [e0].[TestingStrategy], [e0].[TimeIntervalBetweenSubmissionInSeconds]
    FROM [Problems] AS [e0]
    WHERE [e0].[IsDeleted] = 0
) AS [t] ON [e].[ProblemId] = [t].[Id]
WHERE ((([e].[IsDeleted] = 0) AND ([e].[IsDeleted] = 0)) AND (([e].[ProblemId] = @__problemId_0) AND ([e].[UserId] = @__userId_1))) AND (((
    SELECT COUNT(*)
    FROM [ExecutedTests] AS [e1]
    WHERE [e].[Id] = [e1].[SubmissionId]
) > 0) OR [e].[CompilationErrors] IS NOT NULL)
ORDER BY [e].[SubmisionDate] DESC, [e].[Id]
OFFSET @__p_2 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_3 ROWS ONLY

FROM [ExecutedTests] AS [x.ExecutedTests]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT DISTINCT [t1].*
    FROM (
        SELECT [e2].[Id], [e2].[SubmisionDate]
        FROM [Submissions] AS [e2]
        INNER JOIN (
            SELECT [e3].*
            FROM [Problems] AS [e3]
            WHERE [e3].[IsDeleted] = 0
        ) AS [t0] ON [e2].[ProblemId] = [t0].[Id]
        WHERE ((([e2].[IsDeleted] = 0) AND ([e2].[IsDeleted] = 0)) AND (([e2].[ProblemId] = @__problemId_0) AND ([e2].[UserId] = @__userId_1))) AND (((
            SELECT COUNT(*)
            FROM [ExecutedTests] AS [e4]
            WHERE [e2].[Id] = [e4].[SubmissionId]
        ) > 0) OR [e2].[CompilationErrors] IS NOT NULL)
        ORDER BY [e2].[SubmisionDate] DESC, [e2].[Id]
        OFFSET @__p_2 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_3 ROWS ONLY
    ) AS [t1]
) AS [t2] ON [x.ExecutedTests].[SubmissionId] = [t2].[Id]
ORDER BY [t2].[SubmisionDate] DESC, [t2].[Id]

    SELECT [e0].[Id], [e0].[AllowedMemoryInMegaBytes], [e0].[AllowedMinCodeDifferenceInPercentage], [e0].[AllowedTimeInMilliseconds], [e0].[AutomatedTestingProject], [e0].[CreatedOn], [e0].[DeletedOn], [e0].[IsDeleted], [e0].[IsExtraTask], [e0].[LessonId], [e0].[MaxPoints], [e0].[ModifiedOn], [e0].[Name], [e0].[OrderBy], [e0].[SubmissionType], [e0].[TestingStrategy], [e0].[TimeIntervalBetweenSubmissionInSeconds]

FROM [Contests] AS [e]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [e0].*
    FROM [Lessons] AS [e0]
    WHERE [e0].[IsDeleted] = 0
) AS [t] ON [e].[LessonId] = [t].[Id]

    FROM [Practices] AS [e1]

SELECT [e].[EndTime], [e].[LessonId], [t0].[Id] AS [LessonPracticeId], [e].[Name]
FROM [Contests] AS [e]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [e0].*
    FROM [Lessons] AS [e0]
    WHERE [e0].[IsDeleted] = 0
) AS [t] ON [e].[LessonId] = [t].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [e1].*
    FROM [Practices] AS [e1]
    WHERE [e1].[IsDeleted] = 0
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[LessonId]

INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [e0].[Id], [e0].[AllowedMemoryInMegaBytes], [e0].[AllowedMinCodeDifferenceInPercentage], [e0].[AllowedTimeInMilliseconds], [e0].[AutomatedTestingProject], [e0].[CreatedOn], [e0].[DeletedOn], [e0].[IsDeleted], [e0].[IsExtraTask], [e0].[LessonId], [e0].[MaxPoints], [e0].[ModifiedOn], [e0].[Name], [e0].[OrderBy], [e0].[SubmissionType], [e0].[TestingStrategy], [e0].[TimeIntervalBetweenSubmissionInSeconds]

FROM [ExecutedTests] AS [x.ExecutedTests]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT DISTINCT [t1].*
    FROM (
        SELECT [e2].[Id], [e2].[SubmisionDate]
        FROM [Submissions] AS [e2]
        INNER JOIN (
            SELECT [e3].*
            FROM [Problems] AS [e3]
            WHERE [e3].[IsDeleted] = 0
        ) AS [t0] ON [e2].[ProblemId] = [t0].[Id]
        WHERE ((([e2].[IsDeleted] = 0) AND ([e2].[IsDeleted] = 0)) AND (([e2].[ProblemId] = @__problemId_0) AND ([e2].[UserId] = @__userId_1))) AND (((

            WHERE [e2].[Id] = [e4].[SubmissionId]

        ORDER BY [e2].[SubmisionDate] DESC, [e2].[Id]
        OFFSET @__p_2 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_3 ROWS ONLY
    ) AS [t1]
) AS [t2] ON [x.ExecutedTests].[SubmissionId] = [t2].[Id]
ORDER BY [t2].[SubmisionDate] DESC, [t2].[Id]

    FROM [Submissions] AS [e1]

        FROM [Problems] AS [e2]

SELECT [e].[EndTime], [e].[LessonId], [t0].[Id] AS [LessonPracticeId], [e].[Name]
FROM [Contests] AS [e]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [e0].*
    FROM [Lessons] AS [e0]
    WHERE [e0].[IsDeleted] = 0
) AS [t] ON [e].[LessonId] = [t].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [e1].*
    FROM [Practices] AS [e1]
    WHERE [e1].[IsDeleted] = 0
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[LessonId]
